0 battles of the film's 3 main characters. \n \nThe player watches the video and hits the correct direction or button at the right time to achieve success. The visual cues of the movie suggest the correct buttons. For example, when the Masked Rider punches, the player should press the Punch button. If he dodges left on screen, the player should press the left direction pad. Correct timing hits the enemy harder, lowering their health bar. Failure reduces the players health.","collection":3146,"popularity":1.0,"games":[19565,2558,3292,14763,34919,51464,16468,36608,51525,3285],"tags":[1,268435463,536870926,536873299,536875049,536875054,536875289,536875348,536875426,536876663,536876901,536880072],"category":0,"keywords":[14,2387,4137,4142,4377,4436,4514,5751,5989,9160],"themes":[1],"genres":[7],"first_release_date":760060800000,"platforms":[78],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":78,"date":760060800000,"region":8,"human":"1994-Feb-01","y":1994,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/bumhgaeutjrqtzmu3irm.jpg","cloudinary_id":"bumhgaeutjrqtzmu3irm","width":1539,"height":2156},"esrb":{"rating":5}},{"id":46410,"name":"The San Diego Zoo Presents: The Animals!","slug":"the-san-diego-zoo-presents-the-animals","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/the-san-diego-zoo-presents-the-animals","created_at":1499546104347,"updated_at":1515790762653,"summary":"Breakthrough video-with-sound technology in The Animals! lets you see and hear over 200 exotic mammals, birds, and reptiles in over 60 minutes of video clips. Using movies, sounds and stories, The Animals! also brings you the most complete and up-to-date information about our animal neighbors from experts at the world-renowned San Diego Zoo. If you love animals, you'll love The Animals! It's fun and easy for children and adults to explore the vast resources of The Animals! Clicking on the habitat map takes you instantly to the animals that live in one of the earth's major climate zones including: tropi