erns like dinosaur skins, moving water, stripes, dots, or the cool animated stickers to bring your drawings to life!","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,34919,79680,73186,73127,71928,70031,70012,69890,67802],"tags":[1,34,536871446],"category":0,"keywords":[534],"themes":[1,34],"first_release_date":728524800000,"platforms":[78],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":78,"date":728524800000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Feb-01","y":1993,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/j9jqudueqdn58rcbidad.jpg","cloudinary_id":"j9jqudueqdn58rcbidad","width":1539,"height":2156}},{"id":46416,"name":"Marky Mark and the Funky Bunch: Make My Video","slug":"marky-mark-and-the-funky-bunch-make-my-video","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/marky-mark-and-the-funky-bunch-make-my-video","created_at":1499546122311,"updated_at":1513023246834,"summary":"Make My Video: Marky Mark and the Funky Bunch is a video game based on real-time editing of music video footage. The setup is that a brother and sister pair is arguing about what would make the best Marky Mark video. Since they can not agree, they enlist help from some other people: A boxer and his trainer, a trio of teenage girls, the members of a garage band, and their parents. Each group has their ideas about what an ideal Marky Mark video should or should not contain. The specifications normally come in the form of a set of pictures they either do or don't want to see, and perhaps some effects. The game has three Marky Mark videos from which to choose: \"Good Vibrations\", \"I Need Money\", and \"You Gotta Believe\".","collection":4926,"popularity":1.0,"games":[77332,67300,37067,16513,28192,11711,64209,20186,4790,44154],"tags":[268435463,536873861,536875049,536875139,536875140,536875426,536875435,536875751,536875939,536876663],"category":0,"keywords":[2949,4137,4227,4228,4514,4523,4839,5027,5751],"genres":[7],"first_release_date":696902400000,"platforms":[78],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":78,