hter maker 2002, a 2D fighting game engine, much like Mugen. \n \nThe game Started as a hobby and took around 9 years to be completed, from the prototype stage to the final product.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"themes":[19],"genres":[4],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/dqf5qeulquj69udanwvf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"dqf5qeulquj69udanwvf","width":1134,"height":309}},{"id":47037,"name":"OMSI: The Bus Simulator","slug":"omsi-the-bus-simulator","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/omsi-the-bus-simulator","created_at":1499712027273,"updated_at":1515839938536,"summary":"Operate a double-decker bus to transport your passengers in late 1980s West Berlin, Germany. Only containing double-decker buses made in various years and each of them having a complex set of functions, you'll have the realistic experience of driving a bus like no other.","collection":3630,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[40470,44242,54789,18623,22470,29173,22425,26145,55590,55689],"tags":[268435466,268435469,536872060,536872511,536875069,536876701,536879861,536880165,536883143],"category":0,"keywords":[1148,1599,4157,5789,8949,9253,12231],"genres":[10,13],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/f5yberyb0hmymrgy45zp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"f5yberyb0hmymrgy45zp","width":352,"height":500}},{"id":47038,"name":"Combat Mission 3: Afrika Korps","slug":"combat-mission-3-afrika-korps","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/combat-mission-3-afrika-korps","created_at":1499712030069,"updated_at":1515758271502,"summary":"Combat Mission: Afrika Korps is a turn-based computer game about tactical battles in World War II. It is part of the Combat Mission series.","collection":3588,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[29173,55590,19934,18623,640,19301,19847,646,23345,19376],"tags":[268435469,268435471,536870931,536871475,536872019,536872060,536874694,536875137,536876701,536879608,536879615,536879624,536879631,536879632,536879633,536879639,536879640,536879643,536881