987,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Greyfell: Legend of Norman"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/odm0dlnndl4znb9dvcpr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"odm0dlnndl4znb9dvcpr","width":1000,"height":1326}},{"id":47141,"name":"Terra Mango","slug":"terra-mango","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/terra-mango","created_at":1499732847214,"updated_at":1499771349861,"summary":"Terra Mango is an LBS (Location-Based Strategy game) for Android and iOS devices [it really is an MMOLBTDRTS (Massively Multiplayer Online Location-Based Tower Defense Real Time Strategy game), but the guys in marketing said we had to shorten it a bit...]. As a player, you can build virtual towers where real buildings exist, battle with troops, in real space, in real time. Nearly every building in the world can be captured and used to build your team’s base. You can capture your house, your neighborhood, and your city! \n \nYou start off by collecting resources which appear all over the world; these resource are used to build your defenses as well as your army. You can build and upgrade towers on almost any plot of land which has a building on it. From here, you and your teammates battle your way through your enemies’ territories and conquer their land.","storyline":"Daniel stared at his father's leftover equipment from the now-abandoned Project Terra Mango… the pretty lights and top-of-the-line tech fascinated him. He dreamed about completing his father’s work, and spent countless hours imagining there was someone out there listening. Daniel was only 12, but like his father was obsessed with the idea that we were not alone in the universe. His imagination ran wild as he began flipping switches, twisting knobs, turning dials. This is the unknown story of why They are here... \n \nDecades later, alien ships began entering Earth’s atmosphere. At first, contact was peaceful...but then something happened. Computers around the world began malfunctioning. Self-driving cars would crash into each other. Cellphones would overheat and catch fire. Rockets would explode on their launch pads. The humans blamed the Aurayu, but they were battling problems of their own. Their biomechanical immunity implants, which make their long lifespans possible, were failing, and their ships began behaving erratically.  \n \nNeither species really knows who shot first. But what we do know is further attempts by either side to improve their technology to combat these malfunctions and defend themselves only made things worse. Some thing happened. They weren’t created. They weren’t programmed. They just were. They call themselves IO. A bit of human and a bit of Aurayu, this new artificial species assembled an army of their own.  \n \nYou are a combatant of this war. Will you defend your race from the intrusion of your enemies as a Human? Will you exact revenge on your creators as the IO? Or will you conquer the blue marble for the honor of the Aurayu? Collect resources, conquer enemy territory, and build towers to ensure victory for your race. Be the first to claim your neighborhood, town, and city! \n \nChoose a side, and enlist now…before it’s too late. \n \nTerra Mango awaits you.","popularity":2.333333333333333,"tags":[1073741827],"developers":[13103],"game_engines":[404],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[3],"game_modes":[5],"keywords":[464],"themes":[38,41],"genres":[11,15,31,32],"status":3,"platforms":[34,39],"release_dates":[{"category":7,"platform":39,"human":"TBD"},{"category":7,"platform":34,"human":"TBD"}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/i9fh5s4qs4dagpfbb6ou.jpg","cloudinary_id":"i9fh5s4qs4dagpfbb6ou","width":3840,"height":2165}],"videos":[{"name":"Teaser","video_id":"OHHqCrPx0WM"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/pdwbwozcp9gpx2fyvmnf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"pdwbwozcp9gpx2fyvmnf","width":3500,"height":3500},"websites":[{"category":9,"url":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVktivTi-cxGNC0w__ROcZw"},{"