 from PC World and Best Handheld Game from the Associated Press. As of March 31, 2015, all versions of Nintendogs combined have sold 23.96 million copies worldwide, making it second on the Nintendo DS best-sellers list, behind only New Super Mario Bros.[4] Because of Nintendogs' success, Nintendo has made several related products, including Nintendogs toys[5] and a series of Nintendogs trading cards.[6] At E3 2010, it was announced a sequel, titled Nintendogs + Cats, would be released for the Nintendo 3DS.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"genres":[13],"first_release_date":1116633600000,"platforms":[20],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":20,"date":1116633600000,"region":8,"human":"2005-May-21","y":2005,"m":5}]},{"id":47945,"name":"Transformers: War for Cybertron - Decepticons","slug":"transformers-war-for-cybertron-decepticons","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/transformers-war-for-cybertron-decepticons","created_at":1499884766372,"updated_at":1500366257652,"summary":"Transformers: War for Cybertron features two distinct storylines: the AUTOBOT campaign tells a story of heroism to save their home planet against overwhelming odds, and the DECEPTICON campaign tells a story of an unquenchable thirst for power to control the universe.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,43130,17469,36950,23175,28277,27266,63734,72412,63718],"tags":[268435461,268435487],"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[5,31],"first_release_date":1280188800000,"platforms":[20],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":20,"date":1280188800000,"region":8,"human":"2010-Jul-27","y":2010,"m":7}]},{"id":47946,"name":"Sokoban","slug":"sokoban--2","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/sokoban--2","created_at":1499885106677,"updated_at":1500367108032,"summary":"Sokoban est un jeu de réflexion sur Nintendo DS. Ce titre remet sur le devant de la scène le vieux jeu de casse-tête : vous devez sortir plusieurs caisses des différents niveaux, parfois avec des mouvements limités. Le titre pro