ferent different locations. \n3) Game Notifications: Whenever one of my friend start playing i get a notification with the name who is playing. It gives me the decision ability to play right at the moment since i know who is playing. And the notification takes me directly to the game. \n \nThings i would love to see: \n1) Voice: If somehow it was possible to do conversation using voice instead of chat it would be so great. \n \nGame Link: https://foolio.app.link","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[11588,19083,28213,28113,16309,74498,26848,18387,28465,19082],"tags":[27,34,40,268435480,268435482,268435488],"developers":[13123],"publishers":[13123],"category":0,"game_modes":[2],"themes":[27,34,40],"genres":[24,26,32],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/tlvsyyuqgtujfomqjf13.jpg","cloudinary_id":"tlvsyyuqgtujfomqjf13","width":1440,"height":2560},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jdd8bfajiwlt2tprfjf0.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jdd8bfajiwlt2tprfjf0","width":1440,"height":2560},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yggzoassiv3elzjrwyhn.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yggzoassiv3elzjrwyhn","width":1440,"height":2560},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ddt6lkynajbj5xue6dg4.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ddt6lkynajbj5xue6dg4","width":540,"height":960}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rzv9cavfzzsadurki5qc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rzv9cavfzzsadurki5qc","width":1024,"height":500},"websites":[{"category":12,"url":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.paxplay.foolio"},{"category":10,"url":"https://itunes.apple.com/in/app/id1165436383?mt=8"},{"category":5,"url":"https://twitter.com/twitter.com/paxplay"},{"category":4,"url":"https://facebook.com/paxplay"},{"category":1,"url":"http://paxplay.in"}],"multiplayer_modes":[{"platform":39,"offlinecoop":false,"onlinecoop":false,"lancoop":false,"campaigncoop":false,"splitscreenonline":false,"splitscreen":false,"dropin":true,"onlinemax":12},{"pla